content:
Configure users who must have access to OmniStudio business processes without admin privileges associated with the license. Use permission sets together with Roles and Sharing Rules to manage user access levels.

For Read-Only users:

Create an OmniStudio Permission Set Group for Standard Read-Only Users.
Create an OmniStudio Standard Read-Only User Profile.
Assign an OmniStudio Permission Set Group to Standard Read-Only Users.

For Create/Edit users:

Create an OmniStudio Permission Set Group for Standard Create/Edit Users.
Create an OmniStudio Standard User Profile for Create/Edit Users.
Assign an OmniStudio Permission Set Group for Standard Create/Edit Users.

Note that only users with the OmniStudio license should have access to designers and perform actions like building business processes.
title: Setting up OmniStudio Standard User Permission Sets
